129
00:11:56,080 --> 00:11:57,550
I... I do.

130
00:11:59,670 --> 00:12:05,100
♪No time to say goodbye, just like this♪

131
00:12:07,290 --> 00:12:12,880
♪Caressing your face, just like this♪

132
00:12:15,430 --> 00:12:20,760
♪Don't say you're sorry, it's too cruel♪

133
00:12:21,030 --> 00:12:22,200
Perfect.

134
00:12:22,790 --> 00:12:24,480
You remember my ring size.

135
00:12:25,080 --> 00:12:25,920
Of course.

136
00:12:28,080 --> 00:12:29,240
I've always dreamed

137
00:12:29,240 --> 00:12:30,550
